*behave-1.2.3 (03 Aug 2013)

  03 Aug 2013; James Rowe <jnrowe@gmail.com> +behave-1.2.3.ebuild:
  Version bump [801].

  08 May 2013; James Rowe <jnrowe@gmail.com> behave-1.2.2.ebuild:
  Use $PYTHON_USEDEP, where possible.

  17 Mar 2013; James Rowe <jnrowe@gmail.com> behave-1.2.2.ebuild:
  Use virtual/python-json for simplejson handling.

  20 Dec 2012; Matt Leighy <mleighy@gmail.com> behave-1.2.2.ebuild:
  Use ranges for PYTHON_COMPAT readability.

  19 Dec 2012; James Rowe <jnrowe@gmail.com> behave-1.2.2.ebuild:
  Updated for distutils-r1 usage.

  09 Dec 2012; James Rowe <jnrowe@gmail.com> behave-1.2.2.ebuild:
  Removed redundant argparse depend.

  27 Nov 2012; James Rowe <jnrowe@gmail.com> behave-1.2.2.ebuild:
  Supports Python 3.3.

  26 Nov 2012; James Rowe <jnrowe@gmail.com> behave-1.2.2.ebuild:
  Switched to EAPI-5.

  01 Nov 2012; James Rowe <jnrowe@gmail.com> behave-1.2.2.ebuild:
  Switched to virtual/python-argparse.

  25 Oct 2012; James Rowe <jnrowe@gmail.com> -behave-1.1.0.ebuild,
  -files/behave-1.1.0-dont_install_global_test.patch, behave-1.2.2.ebuild:
